#, python-format
msgid ""
"Std.: Stock behavior.<br>MAIN+: ACC MAIN on = Display ON.<br>OP+: OP enabled "
"= Display ON.<br>MAIN-: ACC MAIN on = Display OFF<br>OP-: OP enabled = "
"Display OFF."
